00:28:12,294 --> 00:28:13,995
Has anybody ever played this game?

648
00:28:13,995 --> 00:28:15,375
This is way back.

649
00:28:15,375 --> 00:28:16,095
This is a great game.

650
00:28:16,095 --> 00:28:18,076
You know, it had multi-scale gameplay,

651
00:28:18,076 --> 00:28:19,576
flying around the galaxy.

652
00:28:19,576 --> 00:28:20,517
Uh, Elite, of course.

653
00:28:20,517 --> 00:28:20,577
Um...

654
00:28:20,577 --> 00:28:22,757
Cosmic Osmo,

655
00:28:22,757 --> 00:28:24,678
which might seem like an odd choice,

656
00:28:25,054 --> 00:28:28,195
But that was a great game, too, in a differentin a kind of a toy sense.

657
00:28:28,195 --> 00:28:31,256
And then kind of more offbeat things, Microsoft Space Simulator,

658
00:28:31,256 --> 00:28:34,417
which was not a great game, but it was a really fun toy if you were into space.

