00:28:34,417 --> 00:28:36,617
The kind of more recent version of that is this thing, Celestia,

660
00:28:36,617 --> 00:28:39,118
which if you're into astronomy, you really should download this.

661
00:28:39,118 --> 00:28:42,779
It's a free download, and it's got great plug-ins, and it's really cool.

662
00:28:42,779 --> 00:28:44,900
Homeworld, of course, the visuals, the gameplay.

