993
00:43:55,910 --> 00:43:56,010
Um...

994
00:43:56,693 --> 00:43:58,674
Which is not to take anything away from the astronauts.

995
00:43:58,674 --> 00:44:01,155
I think, you know, living and working in space is, you know,

996
00:44:01,155 --> 00:44:02,975
eventually going to be human destiny.

997
00:44:02,975 --> 00:44:04,656
But for right now, on a limited budget, we're getting this

