00:44:04,656 --> 00:44:07,237
tremendous kind of bang for our buck out of these machines.

999
00:44:07,237 --> 00:44:10,478
As a matter of fact, if you just take the price of the Hubble

1000
00:44:10,478 --> 00:44:14,719
telescope, that equals about one week of the war in Iraq right now.

1001
00:44:14,719 --> 00:44:15,619
And if you took the total cost...

1002
00:44:15,619 --> 00:44:22,201
If you took just what we spent in Iraq so far,

1003
00:44:22,201 --> 00:44:25,382
that would buy a Hubble for every member of the UN.

